body:
There is `GetSessionHandleV2` but no `GetSessionTensorV2`. 

```python
v = tf.Variable(gen_data_flow_ops._get_session_handle_v2(tf.constant(0)))
v.initializer.run()
gen_data_flow_ops._get_session_tensor(v, tf.int32).eval()
# ValueError: Incompatible type conversion requested to type 'string' for variable of type 'resource_ref'
```
